                                <note>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="1" to="2" scheme="folios"/>: In all likeliness part of the old endleaves which were removed and bound with the main text.</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="1r" to="1v" scheme="folios"/>: part of the text De scholastica disciplina, which was included among the works of Boethius in early modern editions (but usually found spurious).</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="2" to="2" scheme="folios"/>: ruled but no text </p>
                                </note>
